description: '''Maidcore''' ({{langx|ru|Мейдкор}}, {{langx|ja|メイドコア}}), also known as '''maid rock''', is an [[underground music|underground]] [[electronic music]] [[microgenre]] and [[Music_community#Online_music_communities|online music community]] aesthetically defined by the prevalence of [[anime girl]] [[French maid]] [[persona|personas]]. Popularized on the [[Russia|Russian]] website [[VK.com]], the genre and subculture are influenced by the [[Otaku#Subculture|''otaku'' subculture]], [[anime and manga fandom]] and [[internet culture]]. Maidcore variously blends [[post-rock]], [[shoegaze]] and [[Witch house (genre)|witch house]].
